title: Water
challenge:
Water, perhaps the hallmark of summertime is going to be our seasonal challenge for this week (and for the Summer season). I know, it's not summer everywhere in the world, so those in the southern side, you get to make believe.

Still, moving, submerged, or solid, there should be a lot of variations available with something as versatile as water. How to capture that successfully, as usual, is the great question. :)

title: Wafuku
preface: [Note: Remember to add your entry to the Figure Photography's #figurefridaychallenge section, else if limited in sharing, be sure to at least tag it!]
challenge: Wafuku, or literally "Japanese clothes", is full of tradition and a certain sense of elegance.  Personally, I'm a complete fan for a nice set of traditional clothes, as apparently is +Michael Huttner.  So for this challenge, let's see what figures you can come up with that fit the ideal showcase for a great set of wafuku.  We can leave a little room for interpretation of wafuku to mean simply "traditional" clothes if there's really someone you want to showcase that may fit that ideal.  Interpretation, as always, is completely up to you :).

favorite.title: Rei and Asuka
favorite.blurb:
I don't know what it is, but there's something magical about wafuku and pink, though I may be a touch biased. That certain color of the blossoms just help give that air of cheer and happiness. Combine that with the adorable expressions on their faces and it becomes even better, a whole gamut of emotions and feelings all in one shot.

Color really does play a lot in completing that shot doesn't it?

favorite.title: Sunred and Tachikoma
favorite.blurb: Companions (http://goo.gl/Mlqmq) come in many different shapes and sizes.  In this case, a rather unlikely pairing from different corners of the anime sphere which just work well, especially the one where Sunred is sitting on top of Tachikoma just staring out into the sunset.  It gives a certain sense of peace and establishes that certain bond companions just have when together.
